    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You carve glowing runes into your skin, which you then rub with Chakra-imbued magnesium powder. This seal remains dormant until activated as a swift action, at which point it remains active for 5 rounds, after which it disappears. While active, your nervous system is supercharged, granting the Speed Rank 3 extraordinary ability, a +4 bonus to Will saves and Spot and Listen checks, a blindsense out to 30 ft, a +20 bonus to Balance checks and the ability to Sense Chakra passively, with 30 ft range. You also take 50% additional damage from physical attacks.<br><br>You take 12 damage every time you attempt to perform this technique.</p>\n\n\n\n",
